description: This file contains ASN.1 object implementations related to various public key types (RSA, DSA, DH) and key pair structures, including creation, initialization, verification, encryption, and matching functions for cryptographic operations in a platform-independent manner. It also includes auto-generated code and manual extensions for key management.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_PUBLICKEY
classes.description: A choice structure representing a generic public key with possible variants for DSA, RSA, and DH keys.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_RSAPUBLICKEY
classes.description: A sequence structure representing an RSA public key with modulus and exponent.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_DSAPUBLICKEY
classes.description: An integer structure representing a DSA public key.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_DHPUBLICKEY
classes.description: An integer structure representing a DH public key.

classes.name: ANSC_ASN1_KEYPAIR
classes.description: A sequence structure encapsulating a key type, public key, and private key info.
